quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  25,68,"Wallatheena layadAAoona maAAa Allahi ilahan akharawala yaqtuloona annafsa allatee harrama Allahuilla bilhaqqi wala yaznoona wamanyafAAal thalika yalqa athama"
  25,69,"YudaAAaf lahu alAAathabu yawmaalqiyamati wayakhlud feehi muhana"
  25,70,"Illa man taba waamanawaAAamila AAamalan salihan faola-ikayubaddilu Allahu sayyi-atihim hasanatinwakana Allahu ghafooran raheema"
  25,71,"Waman taba waAAamila salihanfa-innahu yatoobu ila Allahi mataba"
  25,72,"Wallatheena layashhadoona azzoora wa-itha marroo billaghwimarroo kirama"
  25,73,"Wallatheena itha thukkiroobi-ayati rabbihim lam yakhirroo AAalayha summanwaAAumyana"
  25,74,"Wallatheena yaqooloona rabbanahab lana min azwajina wathurriyyatinaqurrata aAAyunin wajAAalna lilmuttaqeena imama"
  25,75,"Ola-ika yujzawna alghurfata bimasabaroo wayulaqqawna feeha tahiyyatan wasalama"
  25,76,"Khalideena feeha hasunatmustaqarran wamuqama"
  25,77,"Qul ma yaAAbao bikum rabbee lawladuAAaokum faqad kaththabtum fasawfa yakoonu lizama"
